response.name: Cece Parekh
response.description: Cece is Jess's best friend from childhood and a former professional model. Over the course of the series, she evolves professionally and personally, eventually marrying Schmidt.

response.name: Coach
response.description: Coach is a roommate who leaves in the pilot episode but returns in the third season as a recurring character and stays throughout the series. He is known for his blunt, athletic but slightly awkward demeanor.

response.name: Dr. Sam Sweeney
response.description: Dr. Sam is one of Jess's love interests, a pediatrician with a cool and charismatic attitude, making several appearances throughout the series as her relationship with him waxes and wanes.

response.name: Fawn Moscato
response.description: Fawn Moscato is a politically-driven and determined publicist who dates Schmidt in Season 4. Her ambitions and manipulative tactics often put her at odds with the group.

response.name: Tran
response.description: An enigmatic elderly Asian man who nick communicates with, despite his silent nature. He appears in several episodes providing comfort or counsel without uttering a word.
